#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:1
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "快速开始"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:3
msgid ""
"This example runs a differential-drive robot from a start pose to a goal. "
"Before continuing, [install IR-SIM](install.rst) and verify that it imports "
"successfully."
msgstr ""
"本示例让一个差速驱动机器人从起始位姿运动到目标。在继续之前，请先[安装 IR-SIM]"
"(install.rst)，并确认可以成功导入。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:5
msgid "Create a Python file named `quick_start.py`:"
msgstr "创建名为 `quick_start.py` 的 Python 文件："

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:23
msgid "In the same directory, create `robot_world.yaml`:"
msgstr "在同一目录下创建 `robot_world.yaml`："

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:25
msgid ""
"The YAML file describes the world and robot. Change these values later to "
"customize the scene."
msgstr "该 YAML 文件描述世界和机器人。之后可修改这些值来自定义场景。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:44
msgid "Run the Python file from that directory:"
msgstr "在该目录中运行 Python 文件："

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:44
msgid ""
"Run the script and a window opens showing the differential-drive robot "
"navigating from its start to the goal:"
msgstr "运行脚本后会弹出一个窗口，显示差速驱动机器人从起点导航到目标："

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:46
msgid ""
"Quick-start simulation — a differential-drive robot navigating to its goal"
msgstr "快速开始仿真 —— 差速驱动机器人导航到目标"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:58
msgid ""
"The loop advances the simulation by `0.1` seconds per step, renders the "
"latest state, and stops early when the environment reports that it is done. "
"For a server or batch job, create the environment with `display=False` and "
"omit the `env.render()` call."
msgstr ""
"该循环每步将仿真推进 `0.1` 秒、渲染最新状态，并在环境报告结束时提前停止。"
"在服务器或批处理任务中，请使用 `display=False` 创建环境，并省略 `env.render()` 调用。"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:52
msgid "Next steps"
msgstr "后续步骤"

#: ../../source/get_started/quick_start.md:54
msgid ""
